# They are created together in every migration file.

# ðŸŒŸ HOW THEY ARE RELATED
# âœ” 1. upgrade() = apply the change
# âœ” 2. downgrade() = reverse the same change

# Example:

# upgrade():
# add age column

# downgrade():
# remove age column
# So:

# Downgrade always does the opposite of upgrade

# Downgrade cannot exist without upgrade

